data.description: LOWERED PRICE! Assumable Loan at 2.25%!!! Seller offering up to $15,000 towards Interest Rate Buydown or closing costs; And a Home Warranty! Welcome to Tranquility. Peaceful, Quiet & Friendly Neighborhood. Close to everything. Many updates, including all new transferable lifetime warranty windows, new Lifeproof vinyl plank flooring, newer kitchen appliances, new sink disposal, new water heater, new washer/dryer and new driveway! Move in ready! All appliances included! Have pets? This is perfectly set up for them; gate on stairway, fully fenced, even a ceiling mount with elect outlet in living room for upside down tree! Excellent soil in garden spaces, several cords of wood for the Living Room Fireplace and Family Room Wood Stove. Beautiful mature 95 gallon Saltwater fish tank worth $4k may be optional. Just blocks from Hollydale Elementary. Corner lot of cul de sac.
